{"id": 2227, "genre": 1000, "title": "你是哪种类型的小说阅读者？", "description": "现如今，你看小说的契机都是怎样的？", "record_count": 17103, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180314172808lqSXOepxywfkRNtn.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-18T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3856, "title": "你是哪种类型的小说阅读者？", "content": "你是哪种类型的小说阅读者?", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 271108, "content": "地铁路上随便看点轻小说/网文型", "image": "img/option/option/20180318220414tPTIDwG6rulbHFgB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 271109, "content": "顺藤摸瓜型，看完紧跟相关作者/主题/风格的另一部", "image": "img/option/option/20180318220325snZxmHGzbuEKBF1f.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 271110, "content": "主题索引型，科幻来一打，推理悬疑来一打", "image": "img/option/option/20180318220129poryHGLtBi78ZOkR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270551, "content": "故事梗概型，那些名声很大的小说总得知道讲的是什么", "image": "img/option/option/20180314173232HIEBcNSq5n2WL04j.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270556, "content": "原著型，遇到好看的电影/剧/游戏就把原著找来看看", "image": "img/option/option/20180314174422AXgSo64QNawBrmF5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270557, "content": "紧跟作者型，喜欢的作家一出新书就找来看", "image": "img/option/option/20180314174505JjYWkB8hbmKHTS2E.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270559, "content": "大牛/朋友推荐型，信赖的人推荐的书一般不会错", "image": "img/option/option/20180314174710gMzNEPDSsbaQ6BoX.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270560, "content": "权威奖项型，专业的小说奖是绝佳的阅读指南", "image": "img/option/option/20180314174834hprCy6U5AEjwvJeg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270562, "content": "书单收藏型，按照系统书单挑着看", "image": "img/option/option/20180314174933KfRUHeF5bdMt3LCz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270563, "content": "随遇而安型，遇到的话就翻开/点开看看，也不求看完", "image": "img/option/option/201803141750244VhLc2yZ0jHkFasJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270565, "content": "绝缘型，已经记不得最后一次是什么时候看的小说了", "image": "img/option/option/201803141751017Tx19MuBAIZHcSjU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270566, "content": "经典重温型，看过的心头好时不时还拿出来瞅瞅", "image": "img/option/option/20180314175327Dov0FbJHhjLUnYfN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}